<h2>About Us</h2>
	<p>Vanja's Music Shop was founded in 2010. It is located in Blanchardstown, very close to the shopping centre. Initially we just provided services such as piano tuning and guitar stringing.</p>
<p>In more recent time we have decided to open a shop and start selling very specific, high quality musical instruments. We do still offer our other services.</p>
<p>Take a look at our new online shop or visit us in Blanchardstown..</p>


